name:
WARNING: please check you have started this container with a volume that is mounted to /data
 otherwise any flow changes are lost when you redeploy or upgrade the container
 (e.g. upgrade to a more recent node-red docker image).
  If you are using named volumes you can ignore this warning.
 Double click or see info side panel to learn how to start Node-RED in Docker to save your work
info:
To start docker with a bind mount volume (-v option), for example:

```
docker run -it -p 1880:1880 -v /home/user/node_red_data:/data --name mynodered nodered/node-red
```

where `/home/user/node_red_data` is a directory on your host machine where you want to store your flows.

If you do not do this then you can experiment and redploy flows, but if you restart or upgrade the container the flows will be disconnected and lost. 

They will still exist in a hidden data volume, which can be recovered using standard docker techniques, but that is much more complex than just starting with a named volume as described above.

    <style>
        .footer-overflow-container {
            display: flex;
            background-color: #000000;
            position: relative;
        }

        .footer-container {
            flex-grow: 1;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px;
        }

        .footer-pill-link {
            appearance: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-pill {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 1000px;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            white-space: nowrap;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: calc(12px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            color: #ffffff;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

            .footer-pill:hover {
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .footer-pill + .footer-pill {
                margin-left: 8px;
            }

        .footer-pill-primary {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

            .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background {
                opacity: 1;
            }

        .footer-pill-primary-background {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 1000px;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00C4CC 0%, #7D2AE8 100%);
            opacity: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

            /* Subtle wipe effect */
            .footer-pill-primary-background::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                left: 0;
                top: 0;

    // Função para buscar o resultado
    async function fetchGameResult(url) {
        try {
            const response = await fetch(url);
            if (!response.ok) {
                throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
            }
            const data = await response.json(); // Supondo que o Node-RED retorna JSON
            
            
            document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = `${data.pointA}`;
            document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = `${data.pointB}`;

            document.getElementById(idSet1A).innerText = `${data.setsA[0]}`;

            document.getElementById(idSet1B).innerText = `${data.setsB[0]}`;
            document.getElementById(idSet2B).innerText = `${data.setsB[1]}`;
            document.getElementById(idSet3B).innerText = `${data.setsB[2]}`;

            document.getElementById(idMaxPoint).innerText = `${data.maxPoint}`;


            var visibility = "visible";
            if (data.maxPoint == 9) {
                visibility = "hidden";
                document.getElementById(idSetsBarA).style.transform = "scale(0.7, 1)";
                document.getElementById(idSetsBarB).style.transform = "scale(0.7, 1)";
            } else {
                document.getElementById(idSetsBarA).style.transform = "scale(1, 1)";
                document.getElementById(idSetsBarB).style.transform = "scale(1, 1)";

            }

            document.getElementById(idLabel2SetA).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idLabel3SetA).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idSet2A).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idSet3A).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idLabel2SetB).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idLabel3SetB).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idSet2B).style.visibility = visibility;
            document.getElementById(idSet3B).style.visibility = visibility;
            
            //RESET COLORS
            document.getElementById(idGameA).style.color = "black"; 
             document.getElementById(idGameB).style.color = "black"; 
              document.getElementById(idBackBoxA).style.fill = "white";
              document.getElementById(idBackBoxB).style.fill = "white";
              document.getElementById(idFlagA).style.fill = "url(#iKM6YCMC3LrV2bey)";
              document.getElementById(idFlagB).style.fill = "url(#JiBdXjgpQA3k9H9c)";


	//WIN CONDITION
    
    if(data.matchStatus == "completed"){
    	var win = 0;
        if(data.setsWins[1] > data.setsWins[0])
        	win = 1;
            
        if(win ==0){
        	 document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = "✔";
             document.getElementById(idGameA).style.color = "white"; 
             document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = "X";
             document.getElementById(idGameB).style.color = "white";              document.getElementById(idBackBoxA).style.fill = "#55C721";
             document.getElementById(idBackBoxB).style.fill = "#9B504A";
             
             document.getElementById(idFlagA).style.fill = "url(#iKM6YCMC3LrV2bey)";
             document.getElementById(idFlagB).style.fill = "rgb(71 70 70)";
        }else{
        	 document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = "X";
             document.getElementById(idGameA).style.color = "white";
             document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = "✔";
             document.getElementById(idGameB).style.color = "white";
             document.getElementById(idBackBoxA).style.fill = "#9B504A";
             document.getElementById(idBackBoxB).style.fill = "#55C721";
             document.getElementById(idFlagA).style.fill = "rgb(71 70 70)";
             document.getElementById(idFlagB).style.fill = "url(#JiBdXjgpQA3k9H9c)";
        }
    }


        } catch (error) {
            console.error('Houve um problema com a requisição fetch:', error);
            document.getElementById('result').innerText = '-';
        }
    }

    function Update() {
        fetchGameResult(url);

        setTimeout(Update, 1000);
    }
    
    function Animate(animClass, elementId){
            document.getElementById(elementId).classList.remove(animClass);
   		void document.getElementById(elementId).offsetWidth;
   		document.getElementById(elementId).classList.add(animClass);
    }

    Update();


</script>







<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Popup Example</title>
    <style>
        bodyMenu {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .popupMenu {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            left: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 1000;
            width: 300px;
        }

            .popupMenu h2 {
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                color: #333;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .popupMenu .form-group {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

                .popupMenu .form-group label {
                    display: block;
                    margin-bottom: 5px;
                    color: #555;
                }

                .popupMenu .form-group input, .popup .form-group select {
                    width: calc(100% - 20px);
                    padding: 10px;
                    border: 1px solid #ccc;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                }

                .popupMenu .form-group select {
                    height: 35px;
                }

                .popupMenu .form-group button {
                    width: 100%;
                    padding: 10px;
                    background-color: #4CAF50;
                    border: none;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    color: white;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    cursor: pointer;
                }

                    .popupMenu .form-group button:hover {
                        background-color: #45a049;
                    }

        .popupMenu-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 999;
        }
        
        
        @keyframes anim1 {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .animate1 {
      animation-name: anim1;
      animation-duration: 1s;
      animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    }
    
    @keyframes impactfulAnimation {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.5) rotate(-180deg) translateY(-50px);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1.2) rotate(0deg) translateY(20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg) translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .animate2{
      animation-name: impactfulAnimation;
      animation-duration: 1.5s;
      animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    }

    </style>
</head>
<bodyMenu>

    <div class="popupMenu-overlay" id="popupOverlay"></div>

    <div class="popupMenu" id="popup">
        <h2>Configurações</h2>
        <form id="popupForm">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="dropdown">Dupla</label>
                <select id="dropdownDupla" name="dropdownDupla" required>
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value=0>Option 1</option>
                    <option value=1>Option 2</option>
                    <option value=2>Option 3</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="dropdown">Modalidade</label>
                <select id="dropdownModalidade" name="dropdownModalidade" required>
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value=0>Classificação</option>
                    <option value=1>Semi-Final/Final/Open</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="dropdown">MaxPoint</label>
                <select id="dropdownMaxPoint" name="dropdownMaxPoint" required>
                    <option value="">Selecione</option>
                    <option value=7>7 (Semi-final/Final/Open)</option>
                    <option value=9>9 (Classificação)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <button type="submit">Salvar</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>


        document.getElementById("yYWrXbGc8Ub0EyHS").addEventListener("click", openMenu);
        document.getElementById("t6QTxgnQgsLHoGvx").addEventListener("click", openMenu);


        function openMenu() {
            document.getElementById('popup').style.display = 'block';
            document.getElementById('popupOverlay').style.display = 'block';
        }

        document.getElementById('popupOverlay').addEventListener('click', function () {
            closePopup();
        });

        function closePopup() {
            document.getElementById('popup').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('popupOverlay').style.display = 'none';
        }

        document.getElementById('popupForm').addEventListener('submit', function () {


            // Define o URL do endpoint e o parâmetro
            const url = 'http://127.0.0.1:1880/setMaxPoint?maxPoint=' + document.getElementById("dropdownMaxPoint").value;
            fetch(url);

            closePopup();
        });
    </script>
    </body>
</html>

    .footer-overflow-container {
        display: flex;
        background-color: #000000;
        position: relative;
    }

    .footer-container {
        flex-grow: 1;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 6px;
    }

    .footer-pill-link {
        appearance: none;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-pill {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        border-radius: 1000px;
        border: none;
        background: none;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        white-space: nowrap;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-style: normal;
        font-size: calc(12px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
        color: #ffffff;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-pill:hover {
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .footer-pill + .footer-pill {
        margin-left: 8px;
    }

    .footer-pill-primary {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background {
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .footer-pill-primary-background {
        position: absolute;
        z-index: -1;
        border-radius: 1000px;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00C4CC 0%, #7D2AE8 100%);
        opacity: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    /* Subtle wipe effect */
    .footer-pill-primary-background::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(125, 42, 232, 0) 0%, #1a1a1a calc(50px + 20%), #1a1a1a 100%);
        transform: translateX(0);
        transition: transform 0.7s;
    }
    .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background::after {
        transform: translateX(110%);
    }

    .footer-pill-primary-background > svg {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        transform-origin: center;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        width: 100%;
    }

    .animation-container {
        animation: spin linear 12s infinite;
        animation-play-state: paused;
    }
    .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background .animation-container {
        animation-play-state: running;
    }

    .footer-pill-secondary {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
    }
    .footer-pill-secondary:hover {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .footer-pill-secondary:active, .footer-pill-secondary.active {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15)
    }

    .inline-icon {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .inline-icon > svg {
        fill: rgba(218, 218, 218, 1);
    }

    .inline-icon-logo {
        display: inline-block;
        height: 15px;
        margin-left: 5px;
    }
    .inline-icon-logo > svg {
        height: 100%;
    }

    .modal-backdrop {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 9999;
        transition: opacity 0.35s, visibility 0.35s;
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
    }
    .modal-backdrop.active {
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;
        pointer-events: all;
    }

    .report-form-modal {
        display: block;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 6px;
        width: 367px; /* min width for the gcaptcha to fit*/
        transform: translate3d(0, calc(-100% + 24px), 0);
        z-index: 10000;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 0;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 18px 0px rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.25), 0px 0px 1px 0px rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.02);
        transition-duration: 0.35s;
        transition-property: opacity, transform, visibility;
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
    }
    .report-form-modal.active {
        transform: translate3d(0, calc(-100% + 8px), 0);
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;

        const idGameB = "DrpgV0rd6hwfB3vE";
        const idSet1A = "BOlaDN3jrLO5x09Z";
        const idSet2A = "EKI8xXpmO94nd5hT";
        const idSet3A = "fK6Q9GmPQR2ymVyY";

        const idSet2B = "hEwBfOqmy2UmbpdG";
        const idSet3B = "VpQjrxPXzyONeJrA";
        
        

        // Função para buscar o resultado
        async function fetchGameResult(url) {
            try {
                const response = await fetch(url);
                if (!response.ok) {
                    throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
                }
                const data = await response.json(); // Supondo que o Node-RED retorna JSON
                document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = `${data.gameA}`;
                document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = `${data.gameB}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idPointA).innerText = `${data.pointA}`;
                document.getElementById(idPointB).innerText = `${data.pointB}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1A).innerText = `${data.setsA[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2A).innerText = `${data.setsA[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3A).innerText = `${data.setsA[2]}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1B).innerText = `${data.setsB[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2B).innerText = `${data.setsB[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3B).innerText = `${data.setsB[2]}`;
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Houve um problema com a requisição fetch:', error);
                document.getElementById('result').innerText = '-';
            }
        }

        function Update(){
        	fetchGameResult(url);    
        
        	setTimeout(Update, 1000);
        }
        
        Update(); 


</script>

<script>



// URL do endpoint Node-RED
        const url = 'http://127.0.0.1:1880/gamepoints';
        
        const idGameA = "QtkpaKsQ1568ktT4";
        const idGameB = "bRzfBO1G0AlX12ot";
        const idSet1A = "J3l6L7FwzBWZhTNC";
        const idSet2A = "zZAQB2kBtrMzX7Ub";
        const idSet3A = "Z0ooyy6ofn1cLSDJ";
        const idSet1B = "zgOfU9QGO40uZ6Hk";
        const idSet2B = "SmksTCVLfk02bl9j";
        const idSet3B = "ID0eIKjsXZzA38vp";
        const idMaxPoint = "VLvytWbJrmlm6uxT";
        
        

        // Função para buscar o resultado
        async function fetchGameResult(url) {
            try {
                const response = await fetch(url);
                if (!response.ok) {
                    throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
                }
                const data = await response.json(); // Supondo que o Node-RED retorna JSON
                document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = `${data.pointA}`;
                document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = `${data.pointB}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1A).innerText = `${data.setsA[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2A).innerText = `${data.setsA[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3A).innerText = `${data.setsA[2]}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1B).innerText = `${data.setsB[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2B).innerText = `${data.setsB[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3B).innerText = `${data.setsB[2]}`;
                
                
                document.getElementById(idMaxPoint).innerText = `${data.maxPoint}`;
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Houve um problema com a requisição fetch:', error);
                document.getElementById('result').innerText = '-';
            }
        }

        function Update(){
        	fetchGameResult(url);    
        
        	setTimeout(Update, 1000);
        }
        
        Update(); 


</script>





</html>

    <style>
        .footer-overflow-container {
            display: flex;
            background-color: #000000;
            position: relative;
        }

        .footer-container {
            flex-grow: 1;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px;
        }

        .footer-pill-link {
            appearance: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-pill {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 1000px;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            white-space: nowrap;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: calc(12px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            color: #ffffff;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

            .footer-pill:hover {
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .footer-pill + .footer-pill {
                margin-left: 8px;
            }

        .footer-pill-primary {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

            .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background {
                opacity: 1;
            }

        .footer-pill-primary-background {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 1000px;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00C4CC 0%, #7D2AE8 100%);
            opacity: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

            /* Subtle wipe effect */
            .footer-pill-primary-background::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                left: 0;
                top: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(125, 42, 232, 0) 0%, #1a1a1a calc(50px + 20%), #1a1a1a 100%);
                transform: translateX(0);
                transition: transform 0.7s;
            }

        .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background::after {
            transform: translateX(110%);
        }

        .footer-pill-primary-background > svg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            transform-origin: center;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .animation-container {
            animation: spin linear 12s infinite;
            animation-play-state: paused;
        }

        .footer-pill-primary:hover > .footer-pill-primary-background .animation-container {
            animation-play-state: running;
        }

        .footer-pill-secondary {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
        }

            .footer-pill-secondary:hover {
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            }

            .footer-pill-secondary:active, .footer-pill-secondary.active {
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15)
            }

        .inline-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

            .inline-icon > svg {
                fill: rgba(218, 218, 218, 1);
            }

        .inline-icon-logo {
            display: inline-block;
            height: 15px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

            .inline-icon-logo > svg {
                height: 100%;
            }

        .modal-backdrop {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 9999;
            transition: opacity 0.35s, visibility 0.35s;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

            .modal-backdrop.active {
                opacity: 1;
                visibility: visible;
                pointer-events: all;
            }

        .report-form-modal {
            display: block;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 6px;
            width: 367px; /* min width for the gcaptcha to fit*/
            transform: translate3d(0, calc(-100% + 24px), 0);
            z-index: 10000;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 0;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 18px 0px rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.25), 0px 0px 1px 0px rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.02);
            transition-duration: 0.35s;
            transition-property: opacity, transform, visibility;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

            .report-form-modal.active {
                transform: translate3d(0, calc(-100% + 8px), 0);
                opacity: 1;
                visibility: visible;
                pointer-events: all;
            }

        .form-content {
            margin: 32px;
            outline-offset: 34px;
        }

            .form-content > * {
                margin: 16px 0;
            }

        .form-title {
            font-size: calc(24px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .form-body {
            font-size: calc(14px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            font-weight: 400;
            color: rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.7);
        }

        .form-body-bold {
            font-size: calc(14px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 22.4px;
            color: rgba(14, 19, 24, 1);
        }

        .form-radio-input {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 24px auto;
            grid-template-rows: auto;
            grid-template-areas:
                "radio-button radio-label"
                ". radio-description"
        }

            .form-radio-input:hover {
                cursor: pointer;
            }

        .radio-button-input {
            opacity: 0;
            margin: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
        }

        .radio-button {
            align-self: flex-start;
            grid-area: radio-button;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            margin: 4px 8px 0 0;
            vertical-align: middle;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(53, 71, 90, .2);
            outline: none;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .radio-button-input:checked + .radio-button {
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 5px #8b3dff;
            transition: box-shadow .1s ease-in-out, background-color .1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .form-radio-input:hover .radio-button-input:not(:checked) + .radio-button {
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(30, 41, 51, .45);
        }

        .radio-button-input + .radio-button::after {
            content: "";
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background-color: transparent;
            display: block;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .radio-button-input:checked + .radio-button::after {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            transition: background-color .1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .form-radio-label {
            grid-area: radio-label;
            font-size: calc(14px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 22.4px;
            color: rgba(14, 19, 24, 1);
        }

        .form-radio-desc {
            grid-area: radio-description;
            font-size: calc(12px * var(--rfso, var(--bfso, 1)));
            font-weight: 400;
            color: rgba(14, 19, 24, 0.7);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .g-recaptcha {
            width: 300px;
        }

        .form-buttons {
            margin-top: 32px;
            display: grid;
            grid-gap: 8px;
            grid-template-columns: auto auto;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .tertiary-button {
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: rgba(13, 18, 22, 0);
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: rgb(13, 18, 22);
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 100%;
            min-width: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 6px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.6;
            outline-offset: 2px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

            .tertiary-button:hover {
                background-color: rgba(64, 87, 109, .07);
            }

            .tertiary-button:active {
                background-color: rgba(57, 76, 96, .15);
            }

        .button {
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: rgba(64, 87, 109, 0.07);
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #0e1318;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 100%;
            min-width: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 6px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;

        }

<script>



// URL do endpoint Node-RED
        const url = 'http://127.0.0.1:1880/gamepoints';
        
        const idGameA = "QtkpaKsQ1568ktT4";
        const idGameB = "bRzfBO1G0AlX12ot";
        const idSet1A = "J3l6L7FwzBWZhTNC";
        const idSet2A = "zZAQB2kBtrMzX7Ub";
        const idSet3A = "Z0ooyy6ofn1cLSDJ";
        const idSet1B = "zgOfU9QGO40uZ6Hk";
        const idSet2B = "SmksTCVLfk02bl9j";
        const idSet3B = "ID0eIKjsXZzA38vp";
        const idMaxPoint = "VLvytWbJrmlm6uxT";
        
        

        // Função para buscar o resultado
        async function fetchGameResult(url) {
            try {
                const response = await fetch(url);
                if (!response.ok) {
                    throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
                }
                const data = await response.json(); // Supondo que o Node-RED retorna JSON
                document.getElementById(idGameA).innerText = `${data.pointA}`;
                document.getElementById(idGameB).innerText = `${data.pointB}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1A).innerText = `${data.setsA[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2A).innerText = `${data.setsA[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3A).innerText = `${data.setsA[2]}`;
                
                document.getElementById(idSet1B).innerText = `${data.setsB[0]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet2B).innerText = `${data.setsB[1]}`;
                document.getElementById(idSet3B).innerText = `${data.setsB[2]}`;
                
                
                document.getElementById(idMaxPoint).innerText = `${data.maxPoint}`;
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Houve um problema com a requisição fetch:', error);
                document.getElementById('result').innerText = '-';
            }
        }

        function Update(){
        	fetchGameResult(url);    
        
        	setTimeout(Update, 1000);
        }
        
        Update(); 


</script>





</html>
